high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the coffee maker on the table.
Pick up the left knife on the table.
Turn around and walk towards the sink.
Place the knife in the cup that is the closest.
Pick up the cup with the knife.
Turn right, walk a little towards the lettuce on the counter, turn right and head towards the microwave.
Place the cup on the left side of the table next to the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place the cup with a knife on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the brown counter with the knife.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Walk over to the sink.
Place the knife into the cup in the sink.
Pick up the cup from the sink.
Walk over to the microwave.
Place the cup on the cabinet under the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a knife inside it next to the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter on the other side of the kitchen.
Pick up knife from counter
Take the knife to the kitchen sink.
Remove coffee mug from sink
Put knife inside of the coffee mug
Take the coffee mug  to the microwave.
Put the mug down to the left of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a cup and place it next to the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the coffee maker on the counter.
Pick up the yellow knife in front of the coffee maker.
Turn around and head towards the sink.
Place the knife if the cup closest to you in the sink.
Pick up the cup with the knife from the sink.
Turn right towards the wall and then turn right towards the microwave next to the fridge.
Place the cup to the left of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with the knife to the left of the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go across the room to the table.
Pick up the chef's knife on the table.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the chef's knife in the coffee cup in the sink.
Pick up the coffee cup with the knife in it.
Go to the table with the microwave on it.
Set the cup and knife down on the table in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a coffee cup with a knife in it onto the microwave stand.
